列表和元组
列表
>>> simplelist = [1, 2, 3]
>>> simplelist = [0]
>>> simplelist = [1, 2, 3]
>>> simplelist[0]
1
>>> simplelist[1]
2
>>> simplelist[2]
3


>>> stringlist = ['a string', 'b string', 'c string']
>>> stringlist[0]
'a string'
>>> stringlist[1]
'b string'
>>> stringlist[2]
'c string'


>>> emptylist.append(1)
>>> emptylist
[1]
>>> emptylist.append(2)
>>> emptylist
[1, 2]


元组
>>> simpletuple = (1, 2, 3)
>>> simpletuple[0]
1
>>> simpletuple[1]
2
>>> simpletuple[2]
3
元组不能用append函数


